window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Spring is here, and Tav and his clan of survivors set out to clean up from the destruction of Vermont's winter. <br> With no gasoline, they will have to find new ways to travel, and they will cross paths with survivors who were strong enough to make it through the bitter cold.</p> <p>And these new enemies will do whatever it takes to survive the spring.</p>"; 
